room_title: Escape room "CarnEVIL" by Challenge Escape Rooms in New York
room_description: You wake up in the middle of the night to carnival music! Weird, right? Determined to locate the source of the sound, you approach the amusement park and quickly realize that something sinister has taken over this once joyful place. Many that enter here now never make it out alive. Can you escape before the clowns find you?
